Soap Idle.

Jobs:
Marketer: Sells soap automatically for you at the rate of 1 click/second.
Buyer: Buys soap automatically for you at the rate of 1 click/second.

Upgrades:
Better Marketing: Improve chance to sell soap by 20% (compounding).
Mega Marketing: Improve chance to sell soap by 50% (compounding).
Soaper Marketing: Improve chance to sell soap by 100% (compounding).
